							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, I did some further reading through the forum and found that a lot of you don't, or discourage, upgrading combat arts.  I can see why.  Lots of gold for the upgrade, not much value in increased damage, buffs, and debuffs.  Wish I read this stuff a LOT earlier in my career, it would have saved me beaucoup bucks.
<br />

<br />
Dwarrow Nightgaunt
