						<tr>
							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Upgrading Combat Arts, ESPECIALLY your dps attacks is NOT a waste.  I have found that some upgrades are less impressive than others, and I am truly sorry you blew that much coin on evade.  Let me give you just a couple of examples of ones that ARE worth upgrading.
<br />

<br />
Merciless Melody at app1 is 5% Haste.  At app4 it's 10%.  Stealth buffs are worth upgrading because you are more likely to sneak past yellow or orange cons with it.  Now, I can't quote numbers on my dps attacks, but they DID go up SIGNIFICANTLY by upgrading from app1 to app4.  On my previous Bard and my Bard in beta, I had Adept3 for most of my dps attacks, and I guarantee you my dps was better than most other Scouts my level (including most predators).
<br />

<br />
It's a shame, really, but what it comes down to was an unlucky choice of what to use that rare harvest on.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
