							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am a level 26 Brigand, and here are a few things I have found out for my class...
<br />
- my App3 Sneak Attack almost equals the damage of my Adept1 Distracting Blade, although they are seperated by 12 levels.
<br />
- upgrading Ruse from App4 to Adept3 has increased it's damage by about 200 on average.
<br />
- Upgrading Burgle to Adept1 can get me past most orange cons.
<br />
- Upgrading Hidden Shiv form Adept1 to Master1 increased it's damage about 50 on average. Haven't timed the DoT yet.
<br />
- I never saw an increase during my upgrades to Strangling Shot, that is unless I upgraded bow or ammo.
<br />

<br />
These are just a couple of my observations.  And you can see, some are good and some are weak.  But like someone said above me, take the SOE descriptions with a grain of salt.  I hope this was able to keep someone from wasting money <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://eq2players.station.sony.com/en/pplayer.vm?characterId=125799104" target="_blank" class="postlink">Zevere Lyphukdup</a>
